item.title: ASH VS EVIL DEAD: Season 1 (2015) // SCC #127
item.description:
Hop in the Delta, losers: we're going deadite hunting! Garrett & DeVaughn are hitting the road with the Ghostbeaters as we tackle our first TV series "Ash vs Evil Dead". We're discussing its translation to TV, the tone, our favorite episodes, and the evolution of our antihero Ash. Take a hit and pass that spooky shit!

New episodes drop every Tuesday, subscribe so you don't miss out... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/specter-cinema-club/
